_sText:
Not sure how this will be received, but the map is made out of mario textures, I ripped them from Super Mario Bros.  Features of the map include:

Two castles, with surrounding moats (with underwater tunnel)...
An underground, which is very dark and is cool for knife battles.
You can get into the castles by running around the outside wall and jumping onto them from the back.
Real Mario textures.
+ some other random stuff.

I'll see how it is received.  Anyway, download it and play it for yourself.
